  "title": "Customer Service Executive (Logistics / Shipping)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle customer inquiries via phone and email professionally and promptly</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal logistics and operations teams</p></li><li><p>Provide shipment updates and resolve issues efficiently</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate documentation and records</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong customer relationships</p></li><li><p>Update and maintain work task management (<a href=\"http://Monday.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Monday.com</a>)</p></li><li><p>Assist in general administrative and support tasks when needed</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min 2 years of relevant experience</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in customer service (experienced in logistics/shipping/air freight is a must)</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to multitask and work in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Team player with a positive attitude</p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a>.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lee Jia Xiang</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25158171</p>",
